LEGISLATIVE HISTORY
S. 281, the TICKET Act, was introduced on January 28, 2025, by
Senator Schmitt (for himself and Senator Markey) and was re-
ferred to the Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation
of the Senate. On February 5, 2025, the Committee met in open
Executive Session and, by voice vote, ordered S. 281 reported favor-
ably with amendments.
118th Congress
