Senator Cruz (for himself and Senator Cantwell) and was referred
to the Committee on Commerce, Science, and Transportation of the
Senate. On July 27, 2023, the Committee met in open Executive
Session and, by voice vote, ordered S. 1303 reported favorably with
an amendment (in the nature of a substitute). On September 12,
2023, that bill was reported and placed on the Senate Calendar. On
April 11, 2024, Senator Rounds was added as a cosponsor.
