SECTION-BY-SECTION ANALYSIS
Section 1. Short title
This section would provide that the bill may be cited as the
‘‘Transparency In Charges for Key Events Ticketing Act’’ or the
‘‘TICKET Act’’.
Section 2. All-inclusive ticket price disclosure
This section would provide that it shall be unlawful for a ticket
issuer, secondary market ticket issuer, or secondary market ticket
exchange from offering an event ticket for sale unless that issuer:
(1) clearly and conspicuously displays the total event ticket price—
if a price is displayed—in any advertisement, marketing, or price
list where the ticket is offered for sale; (2) clearly and conspicu-
ously discloses to an individual who seeks to purchase an event
ticket the total event ticket price at the time the ticket is first dis-
played to that individual and anytime thereafter during the pur-
